  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Begin your epic adventure as you \"Journey Up\" towards t</strong>he sky</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey deep in a mine with no memories in your databanks or directives in your programming. The only thing you see is a glimmer of light far above you beneath a collapsed mine shaft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each jump and hand hold takes you closer to your goal. Explore different biomes and face different challenges as you journey up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore diverse biomes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome presents new sights and challenges on your way to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Singleplayer or online multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether playing offline on your own or online with upto 4 players you can be sure to have good latency with our cloud based servers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic body physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We model the whole body with our physics system so you can swing with your arms or slide things with your feet and push buttons by physically slapping them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 Game modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on easy mode and you can respawn at your highest checkpoint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on speedrun mode to disable checkpoints and try for the fastest finish time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compare individual zone times and whole game complete times with your friends on steam leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[New] Arm locomotion option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR or Desktop Mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Motion controls or Keyboard Mouse or Gamepad support.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full body physics simulation. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull yourself onto ledges by pushing your hands down and raising your legs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether adventuring solo or with up to 4 players online, keep journeying upwards... and don't look down!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Begin your epic adventure as you \"Journey Up\" towards t</strong>he sky</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Begin your journey deep in a mine with no memories in your databanks or directives in your programming. The only thing you see is a glimmer of light far above you beneath a collapsed mine shaft.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each jump and hand hold takes you closer to your goal. Explore different biomes and face different challenges as you journey up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore diverse biomes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9604955596f8582471d8e266d721d058.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each biome presents new sights and challenges on your way to the top.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Singleplayer or online multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/9e6514d8085ca40eb2780b9817d1080d.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether playing offline on your own or online with upto 4 players you can be sure to have good latency with our cloud based servers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Realistic body physics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/d4ce3e3a53f4b83bba890527f8fbddc9.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We model the whole body with our physics system so you can swing with your arms or slide things with your feet and push buttons by physically slapping them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2 Game modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on easy mode and you can respawn at your highest checkpoint</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on speedrun mode to disable checkpoints and try for the fastest finish time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboards</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compare individual zone times and whole game complete times with your friends on steam leaderboards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[New] Arm locomotion option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VR or Desktop Mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Motion controls or Keyboard Mouse or Gamepad support.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Full body physics simulation. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pull yourself onto ledges by pushing your hands down and raising your legs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.poster.avif?t=1758806400\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.webm?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144110/extras/8d5b42fe0169e983e943fabb62ce6da4.mp4?t=1758806400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether adventuring solo or with up to 4 players online, keep journeying upwards... and don't look down!</p>",
